        <mxCell id="legend" parent="1" style="html=1;rounded=1;arcSize=6;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#B4B2A9;fontColor=#5F5E5A;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=4;" value="&lt;b&gt;Legend&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;━━  MQTT PUBLISH telemetry (sensor data upstream)&lt;br/&gt;┄┄  MQTT PUBLISH cmd / CoAP PUT (commands downstream to actuators)&lt;br/&gt;QoS 1 = at least once (telemetry) · QoS 2 = exactly once (battery cmd) · CBOR = compact binary payload" vertex="1">
